 Music makez me...<br/>{{small|medley of \"Burnitup!\" by [[Janet Jackson]], \"Lose Control\" by [[Missy Elliott]]}}\n|\n* Insomnia\n|-\n! 2017&ndash;18<br/>[https://www.facebook.com/TeamUniqueHSK%2Fposts%2F10154766307320736%3A0]\n|\n* NocTUrne<br/>{{small|composed by Jan Nyberg}}\n|\n* Every Inch of You<br/>{{small|Music: Postmodern Jukebox rendition of \"Creep\" and \"All About That Bass\" }}\n\n* \n|-\n! 2016&ndash;17<br/>\n|\n* TU Goes Ramalama<br/>{{small|\"[[Rama Lama (Bang Bang)]]\" by [[R\u00f3is\u00edn Murphy]]}}\n|\n* \n|-\n! 2015&ndash;16<br/>\n|\n* \n|\n* \n|-\n! 2014&ndash;15<br/>\n|\n* \n|\n* \n|-\n! 2013&ndash;14<br/>{{r|1314 programs}}\n|\n* Great Balls of Fire<br/>{{small|\"[[Great Balls of Fire]]\" by [[Jerry Lee Lewis]]}}\n|\n* Wild and Free\n|-\n! 2012&ndash;13<br/>{{r|1213 wssc}}{{r|1213 programs}}\n|\n* TU flow<br/>{{small|\"[[Nu Flow]]\" by [[Big Brovaz]]}}\n|\n* Living Proof<br/>{{small|\"[[You Light Up My Life: Inspirational Songs#Track listing|Amazing Grace]]\" by [[LeAnn Rimes]] and [[The Help (film)#Music|medley of ''The Help'' soundtrack]]}}\n|}\n\n==Media appearances==\nTeam Unique performed on the season one of the Finnish ''[[Dancing on Ice around the world|Dancing on Ice]]'' on 2 November 2013.{{r|DOI}} They also appeared as background skaters in the December 2013 music video for \"[[Selv\u00e4sti p\u00e4ihtynyt]]\" by Finnish pop singer [[Jenni Vartiainen]].{{r|Vartiainen}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em|refs=\n<ref name=\"1314 wssc qual\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.stll.fi/luistelijalle/huippuluistelu/arvokilpailujen-valintakriteerit/muodostelmaluistelu/|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6NbbA3COo|archivedate=2014-02-23|title=Suomen Taitoluisteluliiton arvokilpailuvalintakriteerit kaudelle 2013-2014|publisher=Finnish Figure Skating Association|language=Finnish|accessdate=2014-12-14}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=hsk-historia>Note: Click \"Historia\".\n*{{Cite web|url=http://www.teamunique.fi/|title=Historia|language=Finnish|trans-ti